description.en: Character-filled cafe fit-out in Fitzroy with heritage-style patterned floor tiles, handmade subway tile feature wall, commercial kitchen anti-slip tiling, waterproofed service areas, and decorative brass tile trims.
description.zh: Fitzroy特色咖啡馆装修，复古风花砖地面、手工地铁砖特色墙面、商用厨房防滑铺贴、服务区防水处理，以及装饰黄铜收边条。
